snippet.textDisplay: Tajdar - e - Haram!! A masterpiece! We college friends keep discussing about the music of this song! Reminds me of old style Hindu pilgrimage songs in Marathi language and gives me a hint that we all are the same, humans! Our best creations are all the same, the food for our souls is the same, irrespective of the religion we belong to! That use of harmonium and table, awesome, too good! The chorus, aahh! <3 Somewhere connects to you so well, you get into a loop! Very well performed by all the artists at Coke Studio Pak as always.. Kudos to Atif to keep up the level of the original, heard that one too (Sabri Brothers - Listen to that one too, the link is floating around in suggestions) Lots of love from a soul first and an Indian next.. Allah bless us all :) God bless us all :)
